products.name: Sofa, Katorp natural
products.description:
Enough Storage

The sofa has storage shelves on all sides and wire mesh for you to hang your items.

Placement

Place the sofa in the middle of the room and the mesh back becomes an attractive detail.

Product Info

  • 10-year limited warrranty. Read about the terms in the limited warranty brochure.
  • Smart shelves for storage on all sides of the sofa. The steel mesh can be used to store things by hanging them up.
  • Can be placed as a focal piece in the middle of the room since the steel mesh at the back will add a nice decorative touch to the room.
  • The sofa is made of separable parts and thanks to smart packaging it's easy to take home.
  • The corner can be placed to the right or left, so you can choose the position that best suits your home.
  • Each piece of furniture has a unique personality since natural marks and traces from the production are fully visible and part of the industrial expression.
  • The design makes this piece of furniture easy to place, easy to use for various needs, and easy to match with other furnishings.
  • The cover is easy to keep clean since it is removable and machine washable.

Good to know

This product may have traces of rust. It is part of the expression of the product and does not affect the quality of the material.
Care instructions
Wood
Wipe clean with a dry cloth.
Wet marks should always be dried off as soon as possible to stop moisture penetration.

Metal
Wipe clean with a dry cloth.

Removable cover
Machine wash warm, normal cycle.
Do not use optical brighteners.
Do not bleach.
Do not tumble dry.
Iron medium temperature, max 300°F/150°C.
Dry clean any solvent except trichloroethylene.

products.name: Wodden Lounge Chair
products.description:
Relax in comfort on this natural linen chaise while you enjoy the decorative upgrade that the elegant piece provides to your living room. The chaise features a tufted button-beautiful diamond design that covers a soft foam cushion that creates an incredibly soft seat. Enhance your home and living decor with this uniquely styled Natural Linen Lounge Chaise Chair. The perfect pick in any glam or traditional aesthetic, this chaise lounge showcases button tufted accents, a scrolled back, and an elegant nailhead trim. Crafted from a solid wood with a kiln-dried frame construction, it features four turned bun feet awash in an espresso finish while up top, it’s upholstered with 100% linen with a single color. It strikes a curvaceous, armless silhouette. Plus, it includes a cylindrical toss pillow.

Features

  • Feature an eye-catching pattern
  • The back of the round head and the front of the round head has a tufted effect
  • Features attractive tufted buttons accents and high-density foam padding in the back and seat offer superior quality and comfort
  • High-density foam padding in the back and seat offer superior quality and comfort
  • Crafted with a kiln-dried hardwood frame construction
  • Perfect for any bedroom, living room, office, or guest room

Product Details

  • Frame Material: Solid Wood
  • Seat Fill Material: Foam
  • Weight Capacity: 700 lb.
  • Assembly Required: Yes
  • Product Warranty: 1 Year
  • Seating Comfort: Medium

Upholstery Material

  • Upholstery Material: 100% Linen
  • Upholstery Material Details: Polyester

products.name: Matheney Panel Double Bed
products.description:
Description

The 1950s were a time of classic lines, simple tastes and solid colors, which we’ve captured here in this stunningly minimalist bed, made from sturdy metal. No matter your style, this bed is designed to fit your bedroom or provide a fun place to sleep for kids big or small. Liven it up with a colorful duvet and throw pillows, hang a decorative mesh canopy on top to add sophistication, or simply use sheets in solid colors and lined patterns for the full vintage effect. No foundation or box spring needed! The metal slats, center rail, and four metal legs offer all the support you need and plenty of comfort all night long.

 

Product Details

  • Frame Material: Metal
  • Headboard Included: Yes
  • Footboard Included: Yes
  • Box Spring Required: No
  • Box Spring Included: No
  • Slats Required: Yes
  • Slats Included: Yes
  • Assembly Required: Yes

products.name: Henley Manual Recliner
products.description:
How can a tried-and-true classic be made better? Just add a reclining function! Poised to become your new favorite piece of furniture, this wingback-style chair combines must-have style with relaxation. Crafted from solid and manufactured wood, its frame sits atop turned legs and is swathed in polyester blend upholstery accented by diamond tufting, rolled arms, and characteristic “wings.” With a push, this design leans back, making the perfect perch for curling up with your latest read or napping the afternoon away.

Product Details

  • Upholstery Material: Polyester Blend
  • Reclining Type: Manual
  • Weight Capacity: 300 lb.
  • Assembly Required: Yes
  • Product Warranty: 90-Day manufacturer's warranty

products.name: Abey Platform Bed
products.description:
Description

Behind every sweet dream is a sturdy bed frame. This simplistic platform bed is all you need to create a soothing, contemporary retreat in your bedroom. Crafted from steel with an open, slatted headboard, it showcases a neutral black hue that effortlessly blends in with a variety of color palettes. Its bottom features pine slats, which allow you to place your mattress directly on top, no box spring required. An Allen wrench is included for assembly.

 

Features

  • Avey collection
  • Strong mattress support prevents sagging and increases mattress life
  • Bed rails hold the mattress in place
  • Feet of bed have rubbers on the bottom
  • Can be used with a box spring
  • Can be disassembled for easy transport
  • Can be used with a spring mattress
  • Warranty coverage: accidental stains, accidental damage
  • Can be used with a memory foam mattress

The colour blocks are enhanced by Kantha-like prints, lending a fresh, novel look to your home.
  • Material: 100% cotton
  • Hand screen printed
  • Top band: Stainless steel eyelets
  • Set of 2 curtains

Brushed upholstery envelopes the sofa, accented by deep button tufting and detail stitching, while sinuous springs support a single removable seat cushion stuffed with medium-firm foam fill.

products.description:
Defined by its bonded leather upholstery and plush foam-filled cushions, this two piece set rounds out your favorite seating group in sophisticated style. Its integrated headrest lends you support and comfort while its exposed wood frame adds a handsome touch to your decor. Use this set to anchor your living room ensemble alongside a streamlined linen-upholstered sofa and matching mid-century arm chairs for a sleek contemporary look. Build on the aesthetic by dotting nearby walls with an oval beveled mirror and abstract canvas prints for an eye-catching display. Round out the room with a glass-and-metal TV stand, then kick up your feet on the ottoman and enjoy the big game or a weekend movie night with friends.

products.name: Nola Rocking Chair
products.description:
Inspired by mid-century modern designs, this charming rocking chair has blended the retro feel of a vintage design with the quality design you'd expect from a contemporary piece of furniture. This chic design while imbuing your space with stylish appeal. The high-back contoured design and ergonomic arms also add an extra pop of charm to this piece. Try setting this chair in an unused corner of your nursery for the perfect seat for rocking your baby or reading to your little ones. Next, build on the crisp contemporary appeal by adding a white shag rug, a white metal bed, and a few polka dotted bean bag chairs. You can also bring a pop of fun to space by painting one wall with chalkboard paint to give your child a place to express their creativity.

products.name: Branham 54" TV Stand
products.description:
For fresh style that gives your room a light and airy feeling, this product for TVs up to 60” and up to 75 lbs is the solution you've been looking for. The upper partitioned media shelf is perfect for storing AV components while sliding doors cover two lower storage compartments with adjustable, reversible shelves that are slotted on one side to hold up to six wine bottles each. Finished in high gloss white with a decorative screen printed fret design on mirror panels, this TV stand elevates the style of any room. With customizable and concealed storage, this versatile TV stand works easily in the foyer as an entry table or in the dining room as a buffet.

Features

  • Sliding doors cover two concealed cabinets, each with one adjustable, reversible shelf that has a side slotted to hold up to six wine bottles
  • Divided upper media shelf
